        text: "## echoes_of_the_marsh_PreBattleScene\n[ConversationText]\n[MidRight][LoadZylthia][MidLeft][LoadIone][FarLeft][LoadRonan][FarRight][LoadJarek]\nZylthia: The Galdoran Marshes are more treacherous than I imagined.\n[MidRight]We must stay alert. The Veil won't be far behind us.\n[MidLeft]Fog like this hides more than just the terrain. We need to be cautious.\n[FarLeft]I can feel the weight of the spirits here. They guard this place fiercely.\n[MidRight]Zylthia: Our goal is the Sunken Temple. We can't let fear hold us back.\n[MidLeft]Right! We have to prove ourselves worthy to face whatever guardian awaits us.\n[FarLeft]Worthy? Or just lucky? Either way, we need a plan.\n[FarRight]Let's move forward, but keep your eyes peeled. The marshes are known for their tricks.\n[MidRight]Zylthia: Together, we can overcome anything. Let's uncover the secrets of this place![X]\n\n\n\n## echoes_of_the_marsh_PostBattleScene\n[ConversationText]\n[MidRight][LoadZylthia][MidLeft][LoadIone][Left][LoadRonan][FarLeft][LoadJarek]\nZylthia! We have to discuss what Sorath revealed to us.\n[MidRight]I know, I can feel the weight of it all. The sigil's true nature... it's more dangerous than we thought.\n[MidLeft]But we have allies now, and knowledge. We can confront the Veil together!\n[Left]I still can't shake the feeling that we're being watched. Thalthor's awakening is imminent, and we must act fast.\n[FarLeft]We need to prepare ourselves for whatever lies ahead. I won't let my past dictate my future any longer.\n[MidRight]Then let's gather our strength and head to the Veil. The future of Eldralis depends on us!\n[MidLeft]Together, we can face any challenge. We won't let fear hold us back!\n[Left]For our home, for our friends, we fight! Let's move out![X]",
